==其他==
「Ori」源自[[希伯來文|希伯來文]]，其含義為「我的光芒」，屬男女通用名稱<ref name="Oriname">{{cite web|url=http://www.behindthename.com/name/ori|title=Behind the Name: Meaning, Origin and History of the Name Ori|work=behindthename.com|publisher=Behind The Name|accessdate=2015-04-11|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110211030/https://www.behindthename.com/name/ori|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲開發人員透露遊戲並未對奧里性別作出定義，對奧里均使用中性代稱，讓玩家有較多想像空間<ref name="Origender">{{cite web|url=http://www.reddit.com/r/xboxone/comments/2yxclb/hi_everyone_its_moon_studios_creators_of_ori_and/cpdto5e|title=Hi everyone! - It's Moon Studios (creators of Ori and the Blind Forest) and Microsoft. Ask them anything!|author=Phisamoe|work=reddit.com|publisher=[[Reddit|Reddit]]|date=2015-03-13|accessdate=2015-04-11|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612032209/https://www.reddit.com/r/xboxone/comments/2yxclb/hi_everyone_its_moon_studios_creators_of_ori_and/cpdto5e|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲也包含了[[彩蛋_(媒體)|彩蛋]]，分別向《[[超級馬里奧兄弟|超級馬里奧兄弟]]》、《[[薩爾達傳說|薩爾達傳說]]》、《[[超級肉食男孩|超級肉食男孩]]》和[[威廉尖叫|威廉尖叫]]致敬<ref name="Egg">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/every-ori-and-the-blind-forest-easter-egg-fans-hav/1100-6426193/|title=Every Ori and the Blind Forest Easter Egg Fans Have Found So Far|author=Daniel Starkey|work=gamespot.com|publisher=[[Gamespot|Gamespot]]|date=2015-03-26|accessdate=2015-04-11|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108105359/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/every-ori-and-the-blind-forest-easter-egg-fans-hav/1100-6426193/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

